          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            I created Vibe Coding as a place to share my knowledge, experiences, and insights with fellow developers. My goal is to publish content that is practical, easy to understand, and immediately applicable to real-world projects.
          </p>
          <div class="flex space-x-4 mt-6">
            <a href="https://twitter.com/vibecoding" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-primary-600">
