                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>RESTful APIs & GraphQL</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About This Blog</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Vibe Coding was created to be a resource for developers of all skill levels. My focus is on:
        </p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="flex">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Practical Tutorials</span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Step-by-step guides that you can follow along and implement in your own projects.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Modern Best Practices</span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Insights into the latest development patterns, tools, and techniques.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Performance & Optimization</span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Tips and tricks to make your applications faster and more efficient.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Visual Learning</span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">Code examples, screenshots, and diagrams to make complex concepts easier to understand.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          If you have any questions, suggestions, or just want to say hello, feel free to <a href="mailto:hello@vibecoding.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">reach out to me</a>. I love hearing from readers!
